      public void setMaxCredits(int maxCredits)
      Sets maximum number of credits for the Student. If the maximum number of credits is less than three or more than eighteen, throws IllegalArgumentException.
      Parameters:
      maxCredits - integer containing maximum number of credits for Student.
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if maxCredits is less than 3 or more than 18.
